metadata.description:
ORDINAL WEED NFT Project: A Unique Opportunity to Connect with Stoners Around the World

As the world becomes increasingly digital, the demand for unique, digital assets continues to grow. Non-fungible tokens (NFTs) have emerged as a popular form of digital asset, allowing people to own and trade unique, one-of-a-kind items. And now, a new NFT project is taking the world by storm: the ORDINAL WEED NFT Project.

The WEED NFT Project is a unique open edition NFT project that will run until April 20th, 2023 (also known as 420). The project is centered around marijuana and the culture that surrounds it, offering a fun and exciting way for people to connect with like-minded individuals from around the world.

To get started with the ORDINAL WEED NFT Project, users can purchase an NFT for 0.00420 Ethereum. This NFT serves as a membership pass, giving users access to a variety of perks and benefits within the project.

One of the primary benefits of owning a ORDINAL WEED NFT is the ability to  burn [REDACTED] ORDINAL WEED NFTs at [REDACTED] for a ORDINAL WEED Passport. Each ORDINAL WEED Passport is associated with one of 5000 Ordinals inscribed within the 88k range & on top of that, it allows users to unlock even more benefits and opportunities within the project.

In addition to burning for passports, ORDINAL WEED NFTs also offer the chance to receive random marijuana peripherals and buds. These drops are given to members based on their NFT ID #, who stands a chance to receive valuable and rare drops. Multipliers are in effect for those who own multiple NFTs.

The ORDINAL WEED NFT Project is also designed to help connect stoners from around the world. The project's Discord server serves as a central hub for members to connect, chat, and share their love of marijuana. With members from all over the world, the ORDINAL WEED NFT Project offers a unique opportunity to connect with people from different cultures and backgrounds who share a common interest.

Overall, the ORDINAL WEED NFT Project is a unique and exciting opportunity for anyone interested in marijuana culture and the world of NFTs. With its open edition format, anyone can get involved and start collecting and trading these unique digital assets. And with the ability to burn for higher tier membership passes, receive random drops, and connect with stoners from around the world, there's never been a better time to get involved in the world of marijuana NFTs.

So, what are you waiting for? Head over & start collecting today!
